{"tid":1974593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"怒斥武漢野味播毒 保羅麥卡尼指中國需負責","createTime":"2020-04-16T03:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T05:18:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8eaa2bff8bc27d6536c40d6d69340bf1a9b7994d","tid":1974593,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T03:06:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200416/ARFEHG77Y4AGWDPRIBGFOCYAIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200416%2FARFEHG77Y4AGWDPRIBGFOCYAIE%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=6ab41d6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200416%2FARFEHG77Y4AGWDPRIBGFOCYAIE%2F&h=04fd1d95\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200416/ARFEHG77Y4AGWDPRIBGFOCYAIE/</a><br />\n<br />\n怒斥武漢野味播毒<br />\n保羅麥卡尼指中國需負責<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200416/large/1586959835_025c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200416%2Flarge%2F1586959835_025c.jpg&h=295c805a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正於英國家居隔離的保羅麥卡尼，指武漢濕貨市場應該被禁止，因為食蝙蝠就似中世紀落後行為。<br />\n<br />\n前披頭四成員保羅麥卡尼亦有份於GaGa發起的籌款騷中演出，現年77歲的他最近於訪問中怒斥武漢濕貨市場令武漢肺炎爆發，矛頭直指市場內出售野生動物，嚴重影響社會及人類衞生，他更坦言此舉根本是要與全球開戰，保羅麥卡尼此番無懼敢言獲不少人讚好。<br />\n<br />\n最近保羅麥卡尼接受訪問，他批評像武漢般的濕貨市場應該被禁止繼續出現，應該全面禁止，保羅麥卡尼解釋：「這就像投下了原子彈，因為它影響了全世界。無論哪一個負責，這都是與全球開戰。我真的希望中國政府會說：『OK，我們要令這裏變得超級衞生。』但面對現實吧，食蝙蝠就像是中世紀的行為，牠們都不需要全世界的人死吧，那為何要這樣做呢？這些像中世紀的行為。他們真的要清洗這些行為，這可能引發了它（武漢肺炎），如果不是的話，我真不知道是甚麼（引發武漢肺炎）。」現時保羅麥卡尼正與女兒Mary在英國Sussex進行家居隔離。<br />\n<br />\n除了保羅麥卡尼公然批評內地之外，英國諧星Ricky Gervais日前亦公開怒斥武漢濕貨市場及食野味的行為，他批評：「為人及為動物也好，野生生物的買賣與消費要立刻停止。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：余嬌"},{"pid":"3981aa0e289d6e98b2df6ad21aaf3a3e031b36fc","tid":1974593,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"唔敢屌個政權<br />\n走去屌啲平民食野味"},{"pid":"9a5c5d5b4c204a24d2915fbabdd3fb35534a7716","tid":1974593,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3981aa0e289d6e98b2df6ad21aaf3a3e031b36fc","tid":1974593,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"唔敢屌個政權<br />\n走去屌啲平民食野味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"靚佬brett<br />\nPaul sir肯屌都算好啦"},{"pid":"3e41317126549a6333361e67c2037d14c12e05a8","tid":1974593,"uid":392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3981aa0e289d6e98b2df6ad21aaf3a3e031b36fc","tid":1974593,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"唔敢屌個政權<br />\n走去屌啲平民食野味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"保羅麥卡尼解釋：「這就像投下了原子彈，因為它影響了全世界。無論哪一個負責，這都是與全球開戰<span style=\"color: red;\">。我真的希望中國政府會說：『OK，我們要令這裏變得超級衞生。』</span>但面對現實吧，食蝙蝠就像是中世紀的行為<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea1f2ffbbe1c1a19aa8abf2fc8c1fe126a40c2e","tid":1974593,"uid":266554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/d7/19/f8/d719f865f26a51d6c5c23b11fa93984f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fd7%2F19%2Ff8%2Fd719f865f26a51d6c5c23b11fa93984f.jpg&h=05940558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPaul Sir!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}